css: pre {padding: 4px; background : rgb(220, 220, 220); overflow-x: auto;} pre .color-red {color: red;} pre i, table i {color: green;} .table td, th {border: 1px solid; padding: 5px;} th {font-size: 0.8rem;} table h4 {margin-top: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem;} .tooltip-style {background: rgb(143, 145, 167); font-size: 0.8rem;} .mnull {margin: 0;} .basecolor {color: #000080;} .table .td-code {font-family: monospace; border-top: 0; background : rgb(230, 230, 230);} .img-f-l {float:left; margin:5px;} .table .td-canvas {width:160px;} .flex-container {display: flex; align-items: center;} .flex-container img {padding: 3px; box-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgb(170, 170, 170);} @media (min-width: 320px) and (max-width: 860px) {.flex-container img{width: 40%;}} @media (min-width: 320px) and (max-width: 600px) {.img-f-l{width: 40%;}} .td-25 {width:25%;} .td-60 {width:60%;} .td-50 {width:50%;}
